<p>Letter to hand from Exeter dated March 16th. Sis does not seem too happy but I expect it will be better when things settle down. I would make an endeavour to get over to see them when we get to France, as a face from home might help her to settle down better.</p>
<p>I get weekly despatches from Joye &amp; Ken (always profusely illustrated) who seem quite satisfied with their surroundings. T</p>
